/ip firewall mangle add chain=forward in-interface=ether1 src-address=192.168.10.0/24 content=.googlevideo.com action=add-dst-to-address-list address-list="Youtube" comment="Youtube"

/ip firewall mangle add chain=forward in-interface=ether1 src-address=192.168.10.0/24 dst-address-list="Youtube" action=mark-connection new-connection-mark="Youtube-Conn" comment="Youtube-Conn"

/ip firewall mangle add chain=forward connection-mark="Youtube-Conn" action=mark-packet new-packet-mark="Youtube-Packet" comment="Youtube-Packet"

/queue tree add name="Youtube" parent=global packet-mark="Youtube-Packet" max-limit=10M 

Catatan : 
	- in-interface=ether1 ( ganti dengan interface yg mau dilimit )
	- src-address=192.168.10.0/24 ( ganti dengan address/ip jaringan local yg mau dilimit )
	- max-limit=10M ( ganti dengan bandwith yg ingin anda berikan untuk youtube )
